OL,3,CMotorcyclist dies in collision with
OL,4,Clorry
OL,6,FA man has died following a two-vehicle
OL,7,Fcollision in Co Armagh on Friday.
OL,9,FPolice received a report at around
OL,10,F11.40am of a collision involving a
OL,11,Fmotorcycle and a lorry in the
OL,12,FCoolmillish Road area of Markethill.
OL,14,FEmergency services attended the scene
OL,15,Fwhere the motorcyclist was pronounced
OL,16,Fdead.
OL,18,FThe Coolmillish Road, which was closed
OL,19,Ffor a time, has reopened.
